	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have to agree wholeheartedly: though you should keep all your weapon skills trained, at the higher levels it is better to use a one-handed weapon. As was posted, this is for additional AC in the offhand, but it's also to have two items that can confer stat bonuses. Melee output is negligible for a high-level shaman: HP, AC, and Mana are more important.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
